{"tid":2033141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽到各位手足終於肯大嗌「香港獨立、唯一出路","createTime":"2020-05-24T12:52:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T03:22:01.000Z","uid":10788,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7f67b35c4d838fdef97448dd3d79ec7b5b7e513f","tid":2033141,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T12:52:07.000Z","msg":"香港獨立文宣部<br />\n我哋相信只有香港獨立先係香港嘅唯一出路，沒有主權，所有政治理念到頭來都只能是理念，不能實踐。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKSPD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKSPD&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMnqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=e0f2b2cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKSPD</a><br />\n<br />\n入TG聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QwGhy6L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQwGhy6L.png&h=d209055b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日喺遊行聽到各位手足終於肯大嗌「香港獨立、唯一出路」呢句口號真係好感動。<br />\n<br />\n不過推動香港獨立係一件神聖莊嚴嘅事，所以希望各位除咗能夠宣之於口外，仲可以落手落腳用盡一切必要手段推動。<br />\n<br />\n我相信終有一日，我哋可以用香港國國民呢個身份，向世界宣示主權，而呢一日，其實可能比各位想像中要近。"},{"pid":"87a3d9486a58bc3ce044503faac8ca33515125bc","tid":2033141,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T12:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15dd2804acc4a4d6f328b6747d9ef6c82e139727","tid":2033141,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:22:01.000Z","msg":"推"}]}